	default_raw_text = "It's been 8 days since I entered this room. Dammed rad storm, they won't let me out, won't let me see my family. I'm growing increasingly frustrated with this multitool. I don't know how much longer I can survive here, I've run out of what snacks and water I could find. The hunger is getting worse, and I can feel the thirst growing. If I don't get out of here soon, I fear I won't make it. Damnit, why didn't I learn how to hack airlocks?! I can't die here! I just can't.";
